fol. 3r: ዘመስከረም[᎓] (in red);
fol. 35r: ዘጥቅምት[፡] (in red); 
fol. 41r: ጥቅምት፡ (in black);
fol. 66r: ዘኅዳር[፡] (in black);
fol. 102r: ታኅሣሥ፡ (in black).
They are encircled by thin red and black lines below and above.
